2. Create a PHP program to display the division table using for-loop.
<?php
echo "    1\t2\t3\n";
for ($i = 1; $i <= 3; $i++) {
    echo $i . "\t";
    for ($j = 1; $j <= 3; $j++) {
        echo number_format($i / $j, 2) . "\t";
    }
    echo "\n";
}
?>

OUTPUT:

    1	2	3
1	1.00	0.50	0.33	
2	2.00	1.00	0.67	
3	3.00	1.50	1.00	

